fields.Title: WHIRLING F2 / KLAASJE'S NOTE
fields.Description: She's left you a note on her table

fields.Title: Interfacing: "But not panicked. Deliberate. Focus..."
fields.Dialogue Text: But not panicked. Deliberate. Focused.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""A gift..." The lieutenant turns to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A gift..." The lieutenant turns to the staircase suspiciously, looking for any signs of another presence in the shadows above.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "You look at her rough, jagged handw..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You look at her rough, jagged handwriting on the note. She was in a rush, but not panicked. Deliberate. Focused.

fields.Title: You: "Seems she left in a hurry."
fields.Dialogue Text: Seems she left in a hurry.

fields.Title: You: "What could this *gift* be?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What could this *gift* be?

fields.Title: Klaasje's Note: ""I'm sorry I fucked everyone over...."
fields.Dialogue Text:
"I'm sorry I fucked everyone over.

PS. I didn't kill him.

PPS. Gift upstairs."
fields.Alternate1:
"See you at The Return.

PS. I didn't kill him.

PPS. Gift upstairs."

fields.Title: Half Light: "Just don't walk into another radio..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Just don't walk into another radio trap, okay...

fields.Title: Klaasje's Note: "Next to stacks of bills, you see a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Next to stacks of bills, you see a note -- a few lines jotted down in large, uneven handwriting just as the writer was about to rush out the door.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I am not drawing my gun... yet. Bu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I am not drawing my gun... yet. But I don't like 'gifts'."

fields.Title: Klaasje's Note: "The note does not reply. The jagged..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The note does not reply. The jagged, rough handwriting looks like she was in a hurry.

fields.Title: Volition: "Relax. Not everyone is out to trap..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Relax. Not everyone is out to trap you.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""A trap, probably." He nods confide..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A trap, probably." He nods confidently. "But don't sweat it. You got the Cuno spotting you. Let's go in."

fields.Title: Klaasje's Note: ""I'm sorry I fucked everyone over...."
fields.Dialogue Text:
"I'm sorry I fucked everyone over.

PS. I didn't kill him.

PPS. Gift upstairs."

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Cuno: ""A gift, huh... ?" The kid turns to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A gift, huh... ?" The kid turns to the staircase. "That's fucking suspicious to Cuno."

fields.Title: Klaasje's Note: ""See you at The Return. PS. I di..."
fields.Dialogue Text:
"See you at The Return.

PS. I didn't kill him.

PPS. Gift upstairs."

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "He says he's not, but his hand move..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He says he's not, but his hand moves instinctively toward his holster as he studies the note.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's hardly surprising.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's hardly surprising."

fields.Title: Klaasje's Note: "No response, not even an echo in th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No response, not even an echo in the stuffy room. You notice a silk shirt on the stairs.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah-yeah." He looks around. "Fugi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah-yeah." He looks around. "Fugitive on the run shit. Cuno's seen this shit before."
